name: Sometimes it's the only thing that connects you home...
description:
"Sometimes it's the only thing that connects you home..." is a old project of mine, with an old aesthetic. It is a piece from my ongoing project "A study in 3D".
This was created while I was away from home, and at the time, my phone was the only thing that connected me to my memories and loved ones.  7200x9600 .png
